<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c01"/><p id="pI01p0166c0101">大齊天保九年歲次戊寅二月八日魯思明敬造
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c02"/>夫玄途杳邁。愛馳馹於苦津。太<note n="0166001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31166;＝冥【史】</note><app n="0166001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31166;</rdg></app>虛<note n="0166002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08512;＝寂【史】</note><app n="0166002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08512;</rdg></app>。甘有作於造□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c03"/>照。使昏夜永幽。為<note n="0166003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04490;＝屯【史】</note><app n="0166003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">屯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04490;</rdg></app>雲而翳景。伏寶盈家。為&CB07099;明以□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c04"/>能人。睹出沒之<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>常。<note n="0166004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">狑＝怜【史】</note><app n="0166004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">怜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">狑</rdg></app>六趣之苦毒。懷慈悲於大千。□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c05"/>十方。定靈基於運未之初。吐神源於<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>始之際。披惠□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c06"/>解於<note n="0166005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06332;＝低【史】</note><app n="0166005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06332;</rdg></app>枝。內鏡三明。外運六通。曠<app source="0166002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08512;</rdg></app><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>為。開万法之□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c07"/><note n="0166006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00655;＝鼓【史】</note><app n="0166006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00655;</rdg></app>。一鳴則九會俱悟。故移駕鹿苑。唱四<note n="0166007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31166;＝真【史】</note><app n="0166007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">真</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31166;</rdg></app>之玄。迴<note n="0166008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07276;＝軫【史】</note><app n="0166008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07276;</rdg></app>□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c08"/>宣二常之極。可謂玄宗云舉。眾目備張矣。故能頃濁波．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c09"/>四非會於涅槃。九源以茲斷流。三障用斯雲掃。自非靈．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c10"/>既周。應緣異域。忻&CB31153;覺花。遊神更&CB00528;。遂使真儀匿曜。□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c11"/>栴檀。今正法摧<note n="0166009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13054;＝綱【史】</note><app n="0166009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">綱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13054;</rdg></app>。經像獎世。十力慧日。沉暉唯遠。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>明．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c12"/>斯弘業。紹隆三寶者哉。然摩訶上士。姓魯。名文。字字道．．．。
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c13"/>俾侯於東國。奕世上公。著<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">夫</unclear>春秋。大漢初基。復封世祖．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c14"/>劫。積惠種於遐代。抱明珠以鎮心。佩白日而照物。稟□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c15"/>能建卓爾之願。秀於眾人之上。立希有之功。挺在群□．．．。
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c16"/>空。行合等心。一時俱唱。遂捨伽藍地。<note n="0166010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30961;＝南【史】</note><app n="0166010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">南</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30961;</rdg></app>區立寺置僧□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c17"/>田。於是近者不勸而來。遠方自率而至。合邑千人共□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c18"/>八繡像一區。合有千佛。人中石像兩區。寶車一乘。龍□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c19"/>□得度飾。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">運</unclear>至難辭。時來叵抑。春秋年七十有五。寢□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c20"/>汪汪之風。早令童年。珪璋之稱。遍滿人口。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">纂</unclear>脩父業。□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c21"/>圓滿。巧圖妙狀。八十種好充備。即是正覺。再顯於道□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c22"/>建寶塔三區。昇玉塼以<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">構</unclear>宇。磨碧石而<note n="0166011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30962;＝營【史】</note><app n="0166011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30962;</rdg></app>基。隆崇聳□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c23"/>荊崑請工。極於人□。彫飾綺麗。踰普光之妙<note n="0166012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30963;＝貌【史】</note><app n="0166012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">貌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30963;</rdg></app>。剬琴□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c24"/>抽榦而陵雲。或<app source="0166005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06332;</rdg></app>柯以<note n="0166013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00877;＝蔽【史】</note><app n="0166013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00877;</rdg></app>日。花草色色而斒爛。百&CB00031;□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c25"/>行路者。仰聖顏而徘徊。稽首者。慕靈容而頌歎。其地□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c26"/>則山川之爽塏。土地之沃壤。万物饒演。人豐禮讓。宅□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c27"/>化。六合寧一。中宮內外。宰相群官。州郡令長。忠貞職□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c28"/>彌勒三會。俱逢上首。逮及法界有形。普同斯福。乃作□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c29"/>文像東行。授記彌勒。下濟群盲。戀心仰慕。圖寫真靈。□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c30"/>神。靈相在中。雖未宣化。氣澤流風。其二<note n="0166014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30964;＝茫【史】</note><app n="0166014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">茫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30964;</rdg></app><app source="0166014" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">茫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30964;</rdg></app>易遠。龍運□．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0166c31"/>挺絕。持一&CB07099;雙。其三奇哉大士。唯魯道惠。練解苦空。志□．．．</p>
